                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301209-200-victim1747 t18301209-200-viclabel1122"></join> - I went into his shop on the 18th of November, and saw the prisoner there with his face towards the window; he turned to go out - I said, "Young man, what have you got?" he made no answer - I attempted to follow him, but could not go fast enough; I called Stop thief! and he was stopped.</p>
